msg: Cleaned up PhoneGap BlackBerry I/O classes. Added more function header documentation to PhoneGap.java, hooked in the history stack implementation in ConnectionManager to a private KeyListener class, which triggers on the hardware `Back` button present in all BlackBerry devices.
